@vindex paths-dir-bibliographic-notes
@vindex paths-dir-private
@vindex paths-dir-websites
@vindex paths-dir-personal-bibliography
@vindex paths-dir-PW
These directories are children of @code{paths-dir-dropbox} and contain personal data:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-dir-dotfiles}: the dotfiles repository (default: @samp{Dropbox/dotfiles/}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-dotemacs}: the Emacs subdirectory within dotfiles. Its default is user-dependent, resolved at load time based on the @samp{$HOME} environment variable.
@item
@code{paths-dir-notes}, @code{paths-dir-journal}, @code{paths-dir-wiki}: directories for Org notes, journal entries, and wiki content.
@item
@code{paths-dir-wiki-entries} and @code{paths-dir-wiki-references}: subdirectories of the wiki.
@item
@code{paths-dir-blog}: the blog directory.
@item
@code{paths-dir-anki}: the Anki-related Org files.
@item
@code{paths-dir-archive} and @code{paths-dir-inactive}: directories for archived and inactive content.
@item
@code{paths-dir-android}: files synced with an Android device.
@item
@code{paths-dir-bbdb}, @code{paths-dir-people}: contact databases.
@item
@code{paths-dir-ledger}: plain-text accounting files.
@item
@code{paths-dir-bibliographic-notes}: notes attached to bibliographic entries.
@item
@code{paths-dir-private}: private dotfiles not committed to the public repo.
@item
@code{paths-dir-websites}: website source files.
@item
@code{paths-dir-personal-bibliography}: Bib@TeX{} bibliography files and related resources.
@item
@code{paths-dir-PW}: the PW project directory.
@end itemize

@node Emacs configuration directories
@subsection Emacs configuration directories

@vindex paths-dir-karabiner
@vindex paths-dir-yasnippets
@vindex paths-dir-yasnippets-private
@vindex paths-dir-abbrev
@vindex paths-dir-emacs-var
@vindex paths-dir-emacs-local
@vindex paths-dir-init-default
These directories hold Emacs configuration artifacts:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-dir-karabiner}: Karabiner dotfiles (child of @code{paths-dir-dotfiles}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-yasnippets} and @code{paths-dir-yasnippets-private}: snippet collections (children of @code{paths-dir-dotemacs}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-abbrev}: abbreviation definitions (child of @code{paths-dir-dotemacs}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-emacs-var} and @code{paths-dir-emacs-local}: runtime data directories (children of @code{paths-dir-emacs}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-init-default}: default target for tangled init files (default: the @samp{develop/} profile under @code{paths-dir-emacs-profiles}).
@end itemize

@node Google Drive directories
@subsection Google Drive directories

@vindex paths-dir-pdf-library
@vindex paths-dir-html-library
@vindex paths-dir-media-library
@vindex paths-dir-music
@vindex paths-dir-movies
@vindex paths-dir-finance
@vindex paths-dir-audiobooks
@vindex paths-dir-org-images
These directories are children of @code{paths-dir-google-drive} and contain media and library content:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-dir-pdf-library}, @code{paths-dir-html-library}, @code{paths-dir-media-library}: document and media libraries.
@item
@code{paths-dir-music}: the root music directory, with children @code{paths-dir-music-tango}, @code{paths-dir-music-popular}, @code{paths-dir-music-classical}, and @code{paths-dir-music-to-sort} for genre subdirectories.
@item
@code{paths-dir-movies}: the movies directory (default: @samp{~/movies/}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-finance}: financial documents.
@item
@code{paths-dir-audiobooks}: audiobook files.
@item
@code{paths-dir-org-images}: images embedded in Org files.
@end itemize

