@node Repository directories
@subsection Repository directories

@vindex paths-dir-external-repos
@vindex paths-dir-tlon-repos
@vindex paths-dir-personal-repos
@vindex paths-dir-tlon-todos
@vindex paths-dir-tlon-docs
@vindex paths-dir-babel-refs
@vindex paths-dir-translation-server
@vindex paths-dir-split-git
@vindex paths-dir-all-repos
These directories organize Git repositories by provenance:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-dir-external-repos} (default: @samp{~/source/}): third-party repositories.
@item
@code{paths-dir-tlon-repos} and @code{paths-dir-personal-repos} (both default to @samp{Dropbox/repos/}): organization and personal repositories.
@item
@code{paths-dir-tlon-todos}: Org files for organization task tracking.
@item
@code{paths-dir-tlon-docs}, @code{paths-dir-babel-refs}, @code{paths-dir-translation-server}: specific repositories.
@item
@code{paths-dir-split-git} (default: @samp{~/git-dirs/}): bare @samp{.git} directories for split-worktree repos.
@item
@code{paths-dir-all-repos}: a list aggregating several personal data directories for use in search and agenda commands.
@end itemize

@node CSL directories
@subsection CSL directories

