These directories hold Citation Style Language resources, used by @samp{citeproc-el} and related bibliography tools:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-dir-personal-csl-styles} and @code{paths-dir-personal-csl-locales}: personal CSL files (children of @code{paths-dir-personal-bibliography}).
@item
@code{paths-dir-tlon-csl-styles} and @code{paths-dir-tlon-csl-locales}: organization CSL files (children of @code{paths-dir-babel-refs}).
@end itemize

