@node Org directories
@subsection Org directories

@vindex paths-dir-org
@vindex paths-dir-org-roam
The variable @code{paths-dir-org} specifies the root directory for Org files, intended to be used as the value of @code{org-directory}. The default is @code{paths-dir-dropbox}.

The variable @code{paths-dir-org-roam} specifies the Org-roam directory, intended for @code{org-roam-directory}. The default is the same as @code{paths-dir-org}.

