@subsection Ledger files

@vindex paths-file-ledger
@vindex paths-file-ledger-db
@vindex paths-file-tlon-ledger
@vindex paths-file-tlon-ledger-schedule-file
The ledger variables point to plain-text accounting files:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-file-ledger}: the personal ledger journal file.
@item
@code{paths-file-ledger-db}: the ledger price database.
@item
@code{paths-file-tlon-ledger}: the organization ledger journal.
@item
@code{paths-file-tlon-ledger-schedule-file}: the organization ledger scheduler.
@end itemize

