@node Template files
@subsection Template files

@vindex paths-file-orb-noter-template
@vindex paths-file-orb-capture-template
@vindex paths-file-bookmarks
@vindex paths-file-init-tangle-flags-sans-directory
These variables point to template and configuration files:

@itemize
@item
@code{paths-file-orb-noter-template}: the Org-noter template for bibliographic notes.
@item
@code{paths-file-orb-capture-template}: the Org-roam-bibtex capture template. Uses @samp{$@{citekey@}} as a placeholder in the filename.
@item
@code{paths-file-bookmarks}: the Emacs bookmarks file.
@item
@code{paths-file-init-tangle-flags-sans-directory}: the filename (without directory) for user-specific tangle flags (default: @samp{tangle-flags-pablo.el}).
@end itemize

@node Other identifiers
@section Other identifiers

@vindex paths-tlon-todos-generic-id
@vindex paths-tlon-todos-jobs-id
The variable @code{paths-tlon-todos-generic-id} holds the Org ID of the heading where generic (non-translation-job) TODOs are stored. The variable @code{paths-tlon-todos-jobs-id} holds the Org ID of the heading where translation job TODOs are stored. Both are UUIDs used by @code{org-id-goto} and related functions to jump directly to the right location.

